Haryana
Nov 19, 2014
Domestic Violence, Dowry Harassment
Description:
			Husband and in-laws of a 28-year-old woman have been booked here for allegedly harassing her for dowry.

The victim has alleged that her husband and in-laws have been harassing her for dowry since she got married in 2010, they said.

In a similar incident, a woman has accused her in-laws of demanding dowry from her in Ballabgarh area here.

FIRs have been registered in both the cases and further investigations are on, said police.

